snippet.title: NCFC 2015 - Super Fangame Maker Trailer
snippet.description:
Super Fangame Maker is a 2D Platformer fangame built off of the Super Mario franchise. In this video game, you will click, place, and press together your very own Super Mario fangame level!

With elements from various well-known Super Mario fangames, the very first Super Mario Maker will make it's way onto NCFC 2015, and later MFGG!

Nintendo Community Fangame Convention -
http://www.nintendocfc.com/booth.html?id=108

Mario Fan Games Galaxy -
http://www.mfgg.net/?act=resdb&param=02&c=2&id=31890

This fangame was made in roughly two months, and the editing of this footage was very rudimentary, resulting in a number of visual artifacts. Please understand.

Super Mario Bros. gameplay source -
http://bit.ly/1KqkxBT

All other content credited in-game
